'From Squeak3.1alpha of 4 February 2001 [latest update: #3556] on 10 February 2001 at 12:38:53 am'!"Change Set:		MenuLayer-arDate:			10 February 2001Author:			Andreas RaabFix the layer for menus in stayUp mode."!!MenuMorph methodsFor: 'private' stamp: 'ar 2/10/2001 00:37'!morphicLayerNumber	"helpful for insuring some morphs always appear in front of or behind others.	smaller numbers are in front"	^self valueOfProperty: #morphicLayerNumber  ifAbsent: [		stayUp ifTrue:[100] ifFalse:[10]	]! !